  "detailed_description": "THE YEAR IS 2020. King Corona and his Variants have taken over the globe. All of the medical experts have mysteriously disappeared. It is up to Top Chief with his Non-Medical Experts to race to a vaccine and dethrone King Corona. <br><br>Super Dr. Corona is a Super take on classic 3 match games with a familiar theme.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/564a23ebd735310d0c0bd7cb2753ee94.poster.avif?t=1768135193\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/564a23ebd735310d0c0bd7cb2753ee94.webm?t=1768135193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Match 3 colors - Use blocks as the same color of viruses to destroy them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/046cc6cb1aca7a43a99a0da40ce0b8ce.apng?t=1768135193\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/046cc6cb1aca7a43a99a0da40ce0b8ce.poster.avif?t=1768135193\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=220 /></picture></span><br>Build your SUPERS - Destroy blocks and viruses to fill your SUPER Meter. SUPERS are powerful blocks that destroy viruses in unique ways.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/2005999690504aa8507ac5fd6c708868.webp?t=1768135193\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/2005999690504aa8507ac5fd6c708868.poster.avif?t=1768135193\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=220 /></picture></span><br>Tons of Secrets - Learn 14 Unique SUPERS to beat your opponent faster. Unlock characters in Arcade mode and hidden throughout the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/f6a4d9a73417cde3509025dc226f31e8.avif?t=1768135193\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Blast thru 5 stages of different King Viruses</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Learn techniques to counter their attacks</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Only a Top Doctor will get a High Score</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/c6e3f43dc205a77d1810f931bc7069c6.avif?t=1768135193\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play head to head in a race to the most vaccines</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use Boosters to slow down your opponent or boost you up</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use Taunts to rub it in your opponent</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 2 player local</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/4594a86bbc0b2d3f140e32c686c65630.avif?t=1768135193\" width=616 height=322 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2558320/extras/915f09f2f6f10db2ee193fd2ea2a378e.avif?t=1768135193\" width=616 height=322 /></span>",
